official_title: To expand Medicare coverage to include eyeglasses, hearing aids, and dental care.
short_title: Seniors Have Eyes, Ears, and Teeth Act

summary.text:
Seniors Have Eyes, Ears, and Teeth Act

This bill amends title XVIII (Medicare) of the Social Security Act to expand Medicare coverage to include eyeglasses, hearing aids, and dental care.
